ENTRY            M0678   20260120   20260226   20260226       M143
SUBENT        M0678001   20260120   20260226   20260226       M143
BIB                 13         30
TITLE      Investigation of isomeric ratios in the (gamma,n) and
            (gamma,p) reactions on 120,122m,gSb and 117m,gIn
AUTHOR     (O.A.Bezshejko,I.N.Vishnevsky,V.A.Zhrltonozhsky,
           I.N.Kadenko,V.M.Mazur,V.A.Plujko,N.V.Strilchuk)
INSTITUTE  (4UKRKGU,4UKRIEP,4UKRIJD)
REFERENCE  (J,BAS,69,750,2005)
            English translation of IZV,69,663,2005.
INC-SOURCE (BRST)
FACILITY   (MICRT,4UKRIEP) M-30 microtron.
METHOD     (ACTIV) Induced gamma-activity was measured.
DETECTOR   (GE) Germanium detector.
ANALYSIS   (DECAY) Decay curve analysis.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-S) Statistical errors.
COMMENT    Isomeric ratios for 120m,gSb, 122m,gSb, 117m,gIn
            produced in the reactions 121Sb(gamma,n)120m,gSb,
            123Sb(gamma,n)122m,gSb, 118Sn(gamma,p)117m,g
            with incident end-point energy 15 and 16 MeV
            bremsstrahlung gamma-quanta from M-30 microtron were
            experimentally obtained. Experimental data were
            compared with isomeric ratios calculated using code
            EMPIRE II.
STATUS     (TABLE,,O.A.Bezshejko+,J,BAS,69,750,2005)
            Text on p.751.
HISTORY    (20050907C) Compiled at the Russia MSU SINP
            CDFE by V.V.Varlamov.
           (20100607A) REFERENCE added. DATA-ERR converted to
            ERR-S in Subents 002-004 according to description of
            the source of uncertainties in the article.
           (20260106A) Corrected by VV and SD: REFERENCE, STATUS,
            lowercase.
ENDBIB              30
NOCOMMON             0          0
ENDSUBENT           33
SUBENT        M0678002   20100607   20100610   20100609       M053
BIB                  2          3
REACTION   (51-SB-121(G,N)51-SB-120-M/G,,SIG/RAT,,BRA)
SAMPLE     Natural antimony sample, disk with diameter 20 mm and
            thickness 2 - 3 mm.
ENDBIB               3
NOCOMMON             0          0
DATA                 3          1
EN-MAX     DATA       ERR-S
MEV        NO-DIM     NO-DIM
   16.        .071       .007
ENDDATA              3
ENDSUBENT           11
SUBENT        M0678003   20100607   20100610   20100609       M053
BIB                  2          3
REACTION   (51-SB-123(G,N)51-SB-122-M/G,,SIG/RAT,,BRA)
SAMPLE     Natural antimony sample, disk with diameter 20 mm and
            thickness 2 - 3 mm.
ENDBIB               3
NOCOMMON             0          0
DATA                 3          1
EN-MAX     DATA       ERR-S
MEV        NO-DIM     NO-DIM
   16.        .15        .01
ENDDATA              3
ENDSUBENT           11
SUBENT        M0678004   20100607   20100610   20100609       M053
BIB                  2          2
REACTION   (50-SN-118(G,P)49-IN-117-M/G,,SIG/RAT,,BRA)
SAMPLE     Tin sample enriched to 98.3 %, weight 1 g.
ENDBIB               2
NOCOMMON             0          0
DATA                 5          2
EN-MAX     DATA       ERR-S      -ERR-S     +ERR-S
MEV        NO-DIM     NO-DIM     NO-DIM     NO-DIM
   15.        .09                  .04        .07
   16.        .24       .02
ENDDATA              4
ENDSUBENT           11
ENDENTRY             4
